title: Fabolous and Trey Songz Drop New Mixtape 'Trappy New Years'
text:
Fabolous and Trey Songz teamed up to wish their fans a happy new year by dropping a mixtape titled Trappy New Years . The six-song collaborative project is the second time the duo linked up, previously working together on Trey Songz's 2009 single "Say Aah." Last week, Fabolous released a teaser picture on Instagram of himself and Trey in a Bay Area recording studio working on final touches on the project. The tape comes in advance of Trey's upcoming album Tramaine , which is slated for release in 2017. You can stream Fabolous and Trey Songz's Trappy New Year below.
